\n| 2 | Expose event processor health in /health endpoint | functionality | 3 | 8 | 2 |\\n| 3 | Separate concurrency-limited skips from actual failures | code_quality | 2 | 7 | 1 |\\n| 4 | Log malformed event payload parse failures | code_quality | 1 | 6 | 1 |\\n| 5 | Add event-to-execution correlation tracing | functionality | 4 | 9 | 3 |\\n\\n### Key observations from the codebase:\\n\\n- **The event processor loop (`eventBusTick`) is completely opaque** — it runs every 2s but emits no per-cycle telemetry. You can't tell \\\"no pending events\\\" from \\\"processor crashed.\\\"\\n- **Silent failure at line 79** — malformed JSON payloads are silently downgraded to `{ raw: payload }` with zero logging, hiding upstream integration bugs.\\n- **Concurrency throttling counted as failure** — `failed++` at line 70 conflates normal backpressure with genuine errors, making failure rates misleading.\\n- **No event→execution traceability** — the `executionId` is generated at dispatch but the originating `eventId` isn't threaded through, breaking the debug chain.\\n- **`/health` endpoint is blind to the event processor** — only reports workers and OAuth, missing the event bus entirely.\"}],\"stop_reason\":null,\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":1,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":3338,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":54098,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":3338},\"output_tokens\":1,\"service_tier\":\"standard\",\"inference_geo\":\"not_available\"},\"context_management\":null},\"parent_tool_use_id\":null,\"session_id\":\"a9db3e8a-691f-4ad6-b3a4-71c9dd251f04\",\"uuid\":\"1b08558d-f4ac-4d98-940e-af488dc1a577\"}\n    61→[2026-03-18T12:01:20.209Z] [STDOUT] {\"type\":\"result\",\"subtype\":\"success\",\"is_error\":false,\"duration_ms\":136338,\"duration_api_ms\":118017,\"num_turns\":21,\"result\":\"All 5 ideas saved successfully. Here's the summary:\\n\\n## Observability Scout - Event Bus & Subscriptions\\n\\n**5 ideas created