ch errors). Log throttled events at info level with the current running count and max. Update the final event status logic to distinguish partial-throttled from partial-failed outcomes.\\\",\\\"reasoning\\\":\\\"Lumping concurrency backpressure with real errors makes failure metrics noisy and misleading. An operator seeing high failure rates cannot tell if personas are genuinely broken or just busy. Separating these signals lets the team alert on real failures while monitoring throttling trends independently � critical for capacity planning.\\\",\\\"status\\\":\\\"pending\\\",\\\"user_feedback\\\":null,\\\"user_pattern\\\":0,\\\"effort\\\":2,\\\"impact\\\":7,\\\"implemented_at\\\":null,\\\"created_at\\\":\\\"2026-03-18T12:01:02.804Z\\\",\\\"updated_at\\\":\\\"2026-03-18T12:01:02.804Z\\\",\\\"requirement_id\\\":null,\\\"goal_id\\\":null,\\\"risk\\\":1,\\\"provider\\\":null,\\\"model\\\":null,\\\"detailed\\\":0}}\",\"is_error\":false}]},\"parent_tool_use_id\":null,\"session_id\":\"a9db3e8a-691f-4ad6-b3a4-71c9dd251f04\",\"uuid\":\"639c6b77-7335-48ac-b716-37f42c38f8eb\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-18T12:01:02.824Z\",\"tool_use_result\":{\"stdout\":\"{\\\"idea\\\":{\\\"id\\\":\\\"168032e9-d711-4cc0-8ac0-8ab6e2772800\\\",\\\"scan_id\\\":\\\"1eaf3f6b-6f66-4dbc-a9a0-81a85c760238\\\",\\\"project_id\\\":\\\"c6fd0474-19f1-4223-b6a9-752077c51d3d\\\",\\\"context_id\\\":null,\\\"scan_type\\\":\\\"observability_scout\\\",\\\"category\\\":\\\"code_quality\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"Separate concurrency-limited skips from actual failures\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"In eventProcessor.ts lines 67-72, when a persona hits its concurrency limit the code increments failed++ and logs at debug level. Reclassify this as a separate throttled counter distinct from genuine failures (persona not found, dispatch errors). Log throttled events at info level with the current running count and max. Update the final event status logic to distinguish partial-throttled from partial-failed outcomes.\\\",\\\"reaso